news.title: Wall Street Week Ahead: Investors on watch for AI, economic updates as US stocks steady
news.description: Indian markets are watching for AI profitability signals and economic health indicators. Stocks rebounded, buoyed by expected December Fed rate cuts. However, AI stock volatility, particularly in Nvidia and Alphabet, keeps investors cautious. Upcoming economic reports and consumer sentiment data will be crucial in navigating market uncertainty through year-end.
